          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Rural Housing Opportunity Maximization for Energy Savings Act or the Rural HOMES Act</strong></p> <p>This bill reauthorizes through FY2023 and revises the Farm Security and Rural Investment Act of 2002, including&nbsp;by expanding&nbsp;the rural energy savings program to include loans for replacing a manufactured home with another manufactured home if&nbsp;the replacement&nbsp;would be cost-effective in increasing energy efficiency.</p>]]></text>
